00:04:58.421 --> 00:05:02.071
Lemme get some damn sleep! I've got to bless a Botswanian community tomorrow, for God's sake!

00:05:02.241 --> 00:05:02.732
All day...

00:05:02.741 --> 00:05:06.140
Hey, I wanted to say one thing... In short, I give up. Got it?

00:05:06.279 --> 00:05:09.525
Halt this crap already. Fine, I lost... Whatever...

00:05:09.534 --> 00:05:13.130
Ah-ha! Finally admitted defeated, didn't you?

00:05:13.308 --> 00:05:14.936
The shell is mine!

00:05:16.497 --> 00:05:18.384
HOORAAAAAAAY!

00:05:19.248 --> 00:05:22.082
Hello! Listen to me, people!

00:05:22.632 --> 00:05:24.195
Hear me out, will you?

00:05:24.336 --> 00:05:26.646
I've got an important announcement for all of you!

00:05:27.834 --> 00:05:29.179
In short, people, it was...

00:05:29.485 --> 00:05:31.546
I admit that it was all a joke.

00:05:32.550 --> 00:05:32.984
Got it?

00:05:33.138 --> 00:05:35.267
In short, this entire religion was a joke.

00:05:35.330 --> 00:05:38.209
We just had a bet with the hare--I mean, with the grandmaster...

00:05:38.696 --> 00:05:40.644
