00:05:40.648 --> 00:05:42.925
Anyway, it doesn't matter! I've just given up.

00:05:43.075 --> 00:05:45.661
To put it simple, that's it! All of you are free!

00:05:46.091 --> 00:05:50.807
I'm sorry if someone took it too seriously. That's not my problem. Goodbye, everyone.

00:05:54.255 --> 00:05:55.348
